@startuml AD_LT_05_Manage_Equipment_QC

title AD_LT_05 — Manage Lab Equipment Records & Perform QC Checks

|Lab Technician|
|System|

|Lab Technician|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - AD_LT_00 User Authenticated
  - Equipment records registered in system
  - QC pass/fail thresholds configured
end note

start

:Navigate to Equipment Management module;

|System|

:Display equipment list:\n- Instrument name\n- Last calibration date\n- Next calibration due\n- Status (Active/Maintenance/Out of Service);

:Highlight instruments\noverdue or due within 7 days;

|Lab Technician|

:Select action;

if (Action?) then (Update Equipment Record)
  :Select instrument;

  |System|

  if (Equipment record found?) then (no)
    :Allow technician to\ncreate new record;
    |Lab Technician|
    :Enter instrument name,\nserial number, manufacturer,\ninitial calibration date;
    |System|
  else (yes)
    |Lab Technician|
    :Update calibration date\nand / or maintenance status;\nAdd note;
    |System|
  endif

  :Save update:\ntimestamp + technician ID;

  if (Calibration overdue?) then (yes)
    :Set status = Calibration Required;\nBlock instrument from patient testing;
  else (no)
  endif

else (Record QC Check)
  |Lab Technician|
  :Select instrument or reagent lot;
  :Enter QC result values;
  :Select result: Pass or Fail;

  if (Result = Fail?) then (yes)
    :Enter corrective action taken\n(mandatory);

    |System|

    if (Corrective action provided?) then (no)
      :Block submission;\nCorrective action required;
      |Lab Technician|
      :Enter corrective action;
      |System|
    else (yes)
    endif

    :Block instrument / reagent lot\nfrom patient testing;\nStatus = Out of Service;

  else (Pass)
    |System|

    if (Instrument previously failed QC?) then (yes)
      :Clear QC block;\nRestore instrument for patient testing;
    else (no)
    endif
  endif

  :Save QC record:\ntimestamp + technician ID\n+ corrective action;

else (Schedule Preventive Maintenance)
  |Lab Technician|
  :Select instrument;
  :Enter maintenance date\nand technician responsible;
  |System|
  :Save maintenance task;
endif

|System|

:Display updated equipment list;

|Lab Technician|

:View updated equipment\nand QC status;

stop

@enduml
